DestroyMenu Main-Menu
AddToMenu Main-Menu
+ "urxvt"          Exec exec urxvt
+ "xdmx"            exec $HOME/xdmx.sh
+ "Exit Fvwm"               Quit
+ "Restart My Fvwm"            Restart fvwm -f $HOME/.fvwm/config
+ "Restart Blank Fvwm"            Restart
+ "Restart Computer"       Exec exec systemctl reboot
+ "Turn Off Computer"       Exec exec systemctl poweroff

Mouse 1   R  A  Menu Main-Menu
Key Q A CM Quit
